subject: College World Series
Baseball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Russell Moldenhauer hit his record-tying fourth home run of the College World Series as the Texas Longhorns stopped L.S.U.’s 14-game winning streak and forced a deciding third game Wednesday.
